x4freetext: Self-supporting natural target containing 99.9% of
45Sc with thickness of 3.4 mg/cm2.
Seven Si detectors placed at the end 2-m
time-of-flight tubes were setup at angles ranging
from 22.5. up to 157.5
Simultaneous measurement of time-of-flight and
total deposited energy was used to determine the
masses of the charged particles
